headline: Some of the largest exchanges and financial institutions are embracing betting platforms and crypto. Is it just for the fees?
summary: If legacy financial institutions don’t embrace new technology, their competitors may leave them in the dust.

headline: Is It Too Late to Consider IBKR After the Stock’s 83% Surge in 2024?
summary: Wondering what to do with Interactive Brokers Group stock right now? You are not alone. With the market always shifting and headlines flying, deciding whether to buy, hold, or sell IBKR can feel like high-stakes chess. Over the last year, the stock has rocketed upward by a staggering 83.6%. If you zoom out to the past five years, that turns into an eye-popping 463.1% surge. Even more recently, in the past 30 days, shares have gained 10.4%, though they did dip by 1.9% in just the last week...
